metadata.description: We are continuously amazed at all of the talented builders and innovators that yWhales has had the privilege to engage with. We want to recognize all of the time, energy, and committments that have gone into the yWhales Web3 Ecosystem with a special NFT airdrop. The power and impact that Web3 Communities will have continues to be reinforced. yWhales has been rapidly growing our ecosystem within Web3 space and we are grateful for all of our contributors, members, and key players!
metadata.name: yWhales 2022 Genius
